## ğŸ”¹ 4. Bool Query
Combine multiple conditions.
```json
{
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "must": [         // AND
        { "match": { "title": "search" } },
        { "term": { "status": "active" } }
      ],
      "should": [       // OR
        { "term": { "priority": "high" } }
      ],
      "must_not": [     // NOT
        { "term": { "archived": true } }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

---

## ğŸ”¹ 5. Wildcard Query
Basic pattern matching.
```json
